<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>956</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>qǐ lái zǒu ba 迦南956</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 qǐ lái zǒu ba, zhǔ bì zhěng jiù nǐ.
 qǐ lái zǒu ba, zhǔ yǐ cóng sǐ lǐ fù huó.
 tā bì wèi nǐ nuó kāi, qián miàn zuò zuò gāo shān.
 tā bì wèi nǐ xiū píng, qián miàn tiáo tiáo dà lù.
 zhǐ yào gāng qiáng, bù yào jù pà. nǐ kàn shèng líng de huǒ yàn
 zhèng zài rán shāo. zhèng zài rán shāo. qǐ lái zǒu ba.</lyrics>
</song>